<div class="scrim" data-cart-target="scrim" data-action="click->cart#close"></div>

<aside class="cart-drawer" data-cart-target="drawer" aria-label="Carrito">
  <div class="cart-head">
    <h3>Mi pedido (<span data-cart-target="count">0</span>)</h3>
    <button type="button" class="icon-btn" data-action="cart#close" aria-label="Cerrar">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="cart-empty" data-cart-target="empty">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" style="opacity:.3; margin-bottom:12px;">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4zM3 6h18M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/>
    </svg>
    <p>Tu carrito está vacío.<br>Agrega prendas que te enamoren.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cart-foot" data-cart-target="foot" style="display:none;">
    <div class="checkout-section" data-section="items">
      <button type="button" class="checkout-section-head" data-action="click->cart#toggleSection">
        <span>Productos <span data-cart-target="itemsSummary" class="checkout-section-summary"></span></span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <div class="checkout-section-body">
        <div class="cart-items" data-cart-target="items"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <form data-cart-target="form">
      <div class="checkout-section" data-section="customer">
        <button type="button" class="checkout-section-head" data-action="click->cart#toggleSection">
          <span>Tus datos <span data-cart-target="customerSummary" class="checkout-section-summary"></span></span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="checkout-section-body">
          <label class="checkout-field">
            <span>Nombre y apellido</span>
            <input type="text" data-cart-target="customerName" data-action="input->cart#persistCheckoutInfo" required autocomplete="name">
          </label>

          <label class="checkout-field">
            <span>Teléfono</span>
            <input type="tel" data-cart-target="customerPhone" data-action="input->cart#persistCheckoutInfo" required autocomplete="tel" placeholder="0412-1234567">
          </label>

          <div class="checkout-field">
            <span>Entrega</span>
            <div class="fulfillment-row">
              <label class="size-pill fulfillment-pill">
                <input type="radio" name="fulfillment" value="delivery" data-action="change->cart#toggleFulfillment" required>
                Delivery
              </label>
              <label class="size-pill fulfillment-pill">
                <input type="radio" name="fulfillment" value="pickup" data-action="change->cart#toggleFulfillment" required>
                Retiro en tienda
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="checkout-section" data-section="address" data-cart-target="addressSection" style="display:none;">
        <button type="button" class="checkout-section-head" data-action="click->cart#toggleSection">
          <span>Dirección <span data-cart-target="addressSummary" class="checkout-section-summary"></span></span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="checkout-section-body">
          <label class="checkout-field">
            <span>País</span>
            <select data-cart-target="country" data-action="change->cart#persistCheckoutInfo">
              <option value="Venezuela">Venezuela</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="checkout-field">
            <span>Estado</span>
            <select data-cart-target="state" data-action="change->cart#onStateChange">
              <option value="" disabled selected>Selecciona un estado</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="checkout-field">
            <span>Ciudad</span>
            <select data-cart-target="city" data-action="change->cart#persistCheckoutInfo" disabled>
              <option value="" disabled selected>Selecciona un estado primero</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="checkout-field">
            <span>Dirección</span>
            <textarea data-cart-target="address" data-action="input->cart#persistCheckoutInfo" rows="2" placeholder="Calle, edificio, referencia..." autocomplete="street-address"></textarea>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>

    <script type="application/json" data-cart-target="locationsData"><%= raw locations_data.to_json %></script>

    <div class="totals-row"><span>Subtotal</span><span data-cart-target="subtotal"></span></div>
    <div class="totals-grand"><span>Total</span><span data-cart-target="total"></span></div>
    <button type="button" class="btn-wa" style="width:100%;" data-action="click->cart#checkout">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 0 1-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 0 1-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 0 1 2.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0 0 12.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 0 0 5.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 0 0-3.48-8.413z"/>
      </svg>
      <span data-cart-target="checkoutLabel">Finalizar por WhatsApp</span>
    </button>
    <p style="font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-soft); text-align:center; margin:10px 0 0;">
      Coordinamos pago y envío por WhatsApp.
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>
